WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:06.800
Learning all the festivals, learning to read Hebrew, which took her like 12 months, which is quite normal.

00:00:06.800 --> 00:00:13.840
And then she goes in front of rabbis in London, five rabbis, who asked her a very difficult question.

00:00:13.840 --> 00:00:20.000
They said, if the Nazis and Hitler came back, would you renounce your Judaism to save your life?

00:00:20.000 --> 00:00:22.800
I can't remember what she said. She passed. She passed.

00:00:22.800 --> 00:00:26.080
It was very upsetting that day for her when they asked her that question.

